{"tid":1585711,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"大家會唔會突然有一刻唸返起前度","createTime":"2019-09-21T16:56:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T16:34:52.000Z","uid":314803,"like":58,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"f8bb6cbd0de4283fca2045475ebd9bca873a4e3e","tid":1585711,"uid":314803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T16:56:44.000Z","msg":"我先<br />\n分左手好幾年 <br />\n已經有另一段好穩定嘅感情<br />\n本來都各有各生活 無乜再唸起佢<br />\n但前排執屋<br />\n摷返以前d禮物，video，忍唔住大爆發大喊咗一餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">過咗去就係過咗去了 如果有日係街撞到我唸我而家可以好成熟咁同妳寒喧幾句 知道妳依家過得好過舊時 我係由衷替妳高興<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 謝謝妳令我成長 謝謝妳令我成為一個對自己對家人對現任都懂得負責人的人 謝謝妳出現在我的青春𥚃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"23b67378efe60b90aeb09330928052f7a60fc6bf","tid":1585711,"uid":210182,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T17:29:08.000Z","msg":"乖啦"},{"pid":"0be763095e8a8fd863f652b5373b4e519a7f9dd2","tid":1585711,"uid":303854,"like":48,"dislike":2,"score":46,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T17:30:49.000Z","msg":"求下你唔好再諗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一諗到自己男朋友都會好似你咁諗起前度就好痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19ad089a9af4daa6b65d4f353b6fe91407eaf1e6","tid":1585711,"uid":81381,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T17:32:00.000Z","msg":"唉，自從分左手之後，每晚都忍唔住自己落樓下食枝煙"},{"pid":"2bb71c17e65b7d452844a2d964d4602eb5aa867b","tid":1585711,"uid":28068,"like":19,"dislike":10,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T17:36:17.000Z","msg":"分左手咁耐<br />\n又有新既女朋友<br />\n都唔掉晒舊人既所有野<br />\n賤格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79914d380cfeeff5e0b7da77e212248168b62fc8","tid":1585711,"uid":189870,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T17:43:19.000Z","msg":"冇<br />\n<br />\n分手後個腦剩係想搵個更好既荀盤"},{"pid":"9bce2bcb512ba761a150790300af5a22032299c4","tid":1585711,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T01:41:50.000Z","msg":"有  不過耐家佢應該變左藍屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d54c9ff26512a24ef15cf56076bedb5e43c79dd9","tid":1585711,"uid":314803,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0be763095e8a8fd863f652b5373b4e519a7f9dd2","tid":1585711,"uid":303854,"like":48,"dislike":2,"score":46,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T17:30:49.000Z","msg":"求下你唔好再諗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一諗到自己男朋友都會好似你咁諗起前度就好痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T02:23:21.000Z","msg":"我都唔想架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家女朋友對我好好<br />\n覺得咁樣好對唔住自己現任<br />\n一路都以為自己唔會再有咩留戀<br />\n但一望翻以前啲嘢果下真係忍唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7680024f35cafdca87da35a091db26897b87a3cd","tid":1585711,"uid":314803,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"2bb71c17e65b7d452844a2d964d4602eb5aa867b","tid":1585711,"uid":28068,"like":19,"dislike":10,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T17:36:17.000Z","msg":"分左手咁耐<br />\n又有新既女朋友<br />\n都唔掉晒舊人既所有野<br />\n賤格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T02:29:40.000Z","msg":"我一路都無為意<br />\n當年分手之後就收埋咗係雜物房一路都無再掂<br />\n到而家準備裝修先搬翻出黎<br />\n其實我都知應該要掉了<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但又覺得係自己青春一部分唔捨得掉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"03abd011007e483fc2703881612b51cb6e015b26","tid":1585711,"uid":161649,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T02:45:48.000Z","msg":"之前係街撞到前度 明明望到大家 都扮望唔到<br />\n<br />\n以前明明係最親既人 分手喊生喊死<br />\n到依家只係一個路過既陌生人 感覺好奇怪"},{"pid":"784e6b68a818cdce990f2e9b41ed048533eba488","tid":1585711,"uid":90025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T02:48:12.000Z","msg":"會想八卦"},{"pid":"70df2d2e0f4bb1a7820cd4466215ab3be7271a6d","tid":1585711,"uid":303854,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"d54c9ff26512a24ef15cf56076bedb5e43c79dd9","tid":1585711,"uid":314803,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0be763095e8a8fd863f652b5373b4e519a7f9dd2","tid":1585711,"uid":303854,"like":48,"dislike":2,"score":46,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T17:30:49.000Z","msg":"求下你唔好再諗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一諗到自己男朋友都會好似你咁諗起前度就好痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T02:23:21.000Z","msg":"我都唔想架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家女朋友對我好好<br />\n覺得咁樣好對唔住自己現任<br />\n一路都以為自己唔會再有咩留戀<br />\n但一望翻以前啲嘢果下真係忍唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T03:28:35.000Z","msg":"諗埋呢次唔好諗啦 對女朋友好啲 <br />\n最緊要唔好比女朋友知 知完淨係會唔開心 但又無嚴重到分手仲辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我相信每個女仔都好介意前度呢個人 因為我就係啊屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n間唔中都會係度諗男朋友仲掛唔掛住前度但又唔可以問出口好辛苦啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bab28cb39668e928d7780ea714fb52b2be56553","tid":1585711,"uid":149849,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-2