id":1585711,"uid":31238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T17:58:46.000Z","msg":"會 分左大半年 當初佢話分<br />\n基本上一到夜晚 就會諗起呢個人<br />\n唉"},{"pid":"13b36cff2d4255a0fef32c8755f2b62c1476f58b","tid":1585711,"uid":258683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T18:12:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />會令我諗起果啲ex本身仲有聯絡<br />\n無嘅都唔值得我諗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0833d04d47c9b76ade0536b8131d7bc6fcd17932","tid":1585711,"uid":23203,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T19:58:04.000Z","msg":"會<br />\n諗佢而家究竟死左未 報應黎未"},{"pid":"747ce61d1de6f95eb610eb993ccc581570b4eab0","tid":1585711,"uid":70292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T07:36:58.000Z","msg":"你 最近還好嗎<br />\n對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3b392276c80c4d506b0ef89638461bde03509a0","tid":1585711,"uid":315236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T07:39:49.000Z","msg":"有，屌佢仲差我皮半野未還，比我係條街見到一定追住佢叫佢還錢"},{"pid":"2435ebb6208e1d630faa388b4e41224633e869fe","tid":1585711,"uid":122513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0be763095e8a8fd863f652b5373b4e519a7f9dd2","tid":1585711,"uid":303854,"like":48,"dislike":2,"score":46,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T17:30:49.000Z","msg":"求下你唔好再諗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一諗到自己男朋友都會好似你咁諗起前度就好痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T08:20:47.000Z","msg":"你好，這是《自殺．自療．互助舍》。看來你已累積了不少負面情緒，是嗎？人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。何不暫時停一停，<a href=\"http://到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.help4suicide.com.hk&d=zoPJ6Qh4RBVN8MuZ9mClYpMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=cdfe21fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。 那裡有一些勵志故事和有趣短片，你可以隨心看看。你也可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），讓我們的義工為你加油打氣！<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"b808ad4d2c50da1cd7cd1f7966edae5cba38c5b5","tid":1585711,"uid":96864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T08:33:58.000Z","msg":"呢啲令人作嘔既渣滓少諗為妙<br />\n諗起就反胃"},{"pid":"ae76358d2283445b9229205180cfc1edd769db17","tid":1585711,"uid":158178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T08:39:58.000Z","msg":"到而家都好唔捨得 我ex足足大我十九年 佢而家已經有新男友 但每朝起身都有少少feel唔捨得佢 遲d又要去外國讀書 佢以前對我真係好好 我深明白成功係最好嘅報復 但好多時候做冇講得咁瀟灑 求屌醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ca445c1d1cc07fa9e1d5521c954728fc4939dbd","tid":1585711,"uid":324004,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fa97c26dae96b86c5c400d1cf192a78f067801d5","tid":1585711,"uid":31238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T17:58:46.000Z","msg":"會 分左大半年 當初佢話分<br />\n基本上一到夜晚 就會諗起呢個人<br />\n唉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T08:42:34.000Z","msg":"+1<br />\n臨訓前點都會諗起佢<br />\n仲會諗佢同新女朋友幾咁幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n簡直係折磨"},{"pid":"0d19757c21493512960f2cf806aaa56d4efb9677","tid":1585711,"uid":240406,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T09:24:01.000Z","msg":"分左手差唔多一個月喇<br />\n仲係成日諗起<br />\n以前試過 <br />\n如果漸漸早上同臨訓唔會再諗起呢個人<br />\n就代表你好番了<br />\n其實愛情呢樣野<br />\n根本係一種癮 一種病<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b97f227a4eaff5165e0c6b3f535ea37e8b37d19","tid":